name: SupplyIssue
title: Supply Issue
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains reasons for not providing a prescribed vaccine. This value set contains ICD9CM codes.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify diabetic patients who did not receive a prescribed vaccine due to lack of supply reasons, mapped to QDM attribute of negation rationale.),(Inclusion Criteria: Only include codes which represent a lack of supply reason for a prescribed vaccine not being administered.   Codes used are to be ICD9CM codes only.),(Exclusion Criteria: Exclude codes that do not meet the inclusion criteria.)
